<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长遇到麻烦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，”罗西对朋友们说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要......嗯......在周边放更多的洗车牌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们需要更多的客人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向街道上跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奇怪。”特勒尔看着罗西离开时想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她没带牌子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西来到警察总局所在的广场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察总局只剩下一大块空地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”史密斯侦探在地面上挥着手叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞了下来。“布洛姆市长遇到麻烦了。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”史密斯侦探说，“警察总局也不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开始在口袋里翻找。罗西笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想警察总局不会在您的口袋里吧，侦探先生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好笑吧。”史密斯侦探皱着眉头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在找我的手机。啊，找到了。看看我拍的照片。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探把手机递给罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到照片里有一个高大的银色机器人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"当时我正在向警察总局走去。"史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个机器人突然就出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他喷出一个蓝色泡泡，遮住了警察总局，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后整个大楼就随着泡泡一起飞走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”罗西说，“看起来像是怪人博士干的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。”侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能够发明这种机器人的坏人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有怪人博士这样聪明的人了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，他为什么要带走警察总局和布洛姆市长呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道为什么。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怪人博士想偷别的东西。比如说银行，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>整个城市就没有人能阻止他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道阴影飘过街道。罗西抬头看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的头顶上飘着很多蓝色泡泡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西快速飞上天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用超级视力向离她最近的泡泡看过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是布洛姆市长的房子！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拼命敲打蓝色泡泡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！ 罗西被反弹回来，掉进了远处的一个街区里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦。”罗西叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她看到了蓝色雾气，于是马上站起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一辆车从拐角开过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，噗通！车被泡泡吸进去飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>更多的泡泡出现了。噗通！噗通！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们把汽车、公交车、人，还有别的东西都带走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊。”罗西心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我敢肯定怪人博士的机器人是......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐当！轰隆！罗西向上看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>机器人跺着脚从罗西身边经过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它把一辆车踩碎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西迅速飞向机器人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，还没等她靠近，机器人突然转身。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗通！罗西被泡泡困住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>